00:35:09.500 --> 00:35:18.159
we partnered, we stepped up, we refused to assume that some

00:35:18.199 --> 00:35:24.879
other church, some other group will do it. No, no. We refused

00:35:24.899 --> 00:35:32.179
to miss our opportunity in world evangelism. I'll sum up the

00:35:32.179 --> 00:35:40.859
message tonight by saying it like this. Don't miss it. I went

00:35:40.899 --> 00:35:47.000
to our pastor not long ago. Cassie and I are sent out of the

00:35:47.039 --> 00:35:52.439
People's Baptist Church of McDonough, Georgia. And we had

00:35:52.479 --> 00:35:57.379
our missions conference back in November. In fact, we partnered

00:35:57.379 --> 00:36:03.419
with Macedonia and had Macedonia's biannual national

00:36:03.459 --> 00:36:06.559
conference, and our church hosted our national conference.

00:36:06.599 --> 00:36:10.559
But at the same time, it was our home church's missions

00:36:10.599 --> 00:36:15.399
conference as well. And so Cassie and I prayed about our

00:36:15.439 --> 00:36:20.199
missions offering for the year, and we made a brand new missions

00:36:20.239 --> 00:36:25.919
offering commitment last November. And after we made our

00:36:25.979 --> 00:36:31.359
commitment, I went straight to my pastor, and I said to my

00:36:31.399 --> 00:36:37.699
pastor, preacher, thank you for allowing me an opportunity

00:36:37.739 --> 00:36:43.439
through my local church to give over and above my regular tithes

00:36:43.479 --> 00:36:48.239
and offerings so that others could hear the Gospel. And if

00:36:48.279 --> 00:36:52.339
you're wondering why I did that, I did that because I wanted him

00:36:52.339 --> 00:36:57.439
to know I don't want to miss my opportunity. I don't want to

00:36:57.479 --> 00:37:01.539
miss my opportunity not only to invest, but I don't want to miss

00:37:01.579 --> 00:37:11.719
my opportunity to worship. Don't miss it tonight. I was preaching

00:37:11.759 --> 00:37:15.059
at the Lighthouse Baptist Church in Seagrove, North Carolina,

00:37:15.099 --> 00:37:19.559
where my dear friend Michael Poindexter serves as the pastor

00:37:19.779 --> 00:37:24.759
and has for many years. After I finished preaching that night,

00:37:24.799 --> 00:37:28.959
I encouraged the church family of the Lighthouse Baptist Church

00:37:29.000 --> 00:37:36.199
to not miss their opportunity in missions. After the service was

00:37:36.239 --> 00:37:39.199
over, there was a young lady in the church, and she came to

00:37:39.239 --> 00:37:45.179
Pastor and Mrs. Poindexter, and she said, look, I'm just going

00:37:45.239 --> 00:37:51.339
to be honest with you. In the past, I've missed it. I've had

00:37:51.379 --> 00:37:55.779
an opportunity to invest. I've had an opportunity to worship.

00:37:55.819 --> 00:38:00.419
I've had an opportunity to give horizontally, but also

00:38:00.459 --> 00:38:07.459
vertically, and I've missed it. But pastor, that lady said that

00:38:07.500 --> 00:38:12.939
night, with the help of the Lord this year, I'm not going to

00:38:12.959 --> 00:38:19.899
miss it. I'm not going to miss it. I pray that you'll not miss

00:38:19.939 --> 00:38:23.979
it as well. You've listened so well. Would you bow your head

00:38:24.000 --> 00:38:30.419
with me? My Father, in Jesus' name tonight, oh how grateful I

00:38:30.439 --> 00:38:39.919
am for your Word that teaches us about the opportunity that

00:38:39.940 --> 00:38:49.079
wasn't missed in missions. Oh, I'm thankful for those that made

00:38:49.119 --> 00:38:52.760
up the local church in the Macedonian colony of Philippi

00:38:52.779 --> 00:39:00.159
that refused to miss their opportunity. Lord, if they would

00:39:00.200 --> 00:39:05.200
have missed their opportunity, I would not have had this message

00:39:05.279 --> 00:39:11.519
to preach tonight. And Lord, you have shown us directly from the

00:39:11.559 --> 00:39:16.959
pages of your precious Word tonight, both the blessing and

00:39:17.000 --> 00:39:23.399
the benefit of refusing to miss our opportunity in missions.

00:39:23.440 --> 00:39:28.039
Lord, I don't know. Maybe there is someone here at Fellowship

00:39:28.079 --> 00:39:32.679
Baptist Church, and they would say, like that dear lady at the

00:39:32.700 --> 00:39:36.099
Lighthouse Baptist Church in Seagrove, North Carolina, in the

00:39:36.140 --> 00:39:44.039
past I've missed it. And I can't get that opportunity back. But

00:39:44.079 --> 00:39:49.079
as she said, Preacher, thank you for yet another opportunity this

00:39:49.119 --> 00:39:54.159
year. And by your good grace, I'm not going to miss it this

00:39:54.179 --> 00:40:00.059
year. Maybe someone here at the Fellowship Baptist Church needs

00:40:00.099 --> 00:40:00.959
to make that same

00:40:00.959 --> 00:40:06.199
commitment this year. And so I pray for Pastor Mann as he comes to close the

00:40:06.199 --> 00:40:10.079
service as you lead him to do so that you would give him both wisdom and

00:40:10.079 --> 00:40:16.079
discernment and I'll give you glory and honor and praise in Jesus name, Pastor.

00:40:16.079 --> 00:40:20.839
Would you stand with me? Heads are bowed, eyes are closed. The message and the

00:40:20.839 --> 00:40:25.399
challenge has been direct. Kimberly will play quietly on the piano. Let's be doers

00:40:25.399 --> 00:40:28.999
of the word and not hearers only.

